\ip \bd ?Pa r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e?\bd* K…®taw…ô kaseinein m…ô pa nhag…®n r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e, meinai yermam…ô yame r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e r…®p…ôh n…®niyen nhag…®n. M…ôr…®g r…®kitaw…ô ram…ôs…®k m…ô Aposol Jon r…®m…®rai. In naorahi Jemes, k…®ni iriu kwajikov…ô mir kape Sebedi. In yermam…ô k…®rik ye narmam…ô twelef kape Yesu, k…®ni Yesu rorkeikei p…®k in. Kamni k…®m…ô in r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô m…®n…ô e: N…ôvsaoyen Huv…ô kape Yesu Kristo yame Jon r…®m…®rai, m…®ne 1 Jon, 2 Jon, 3 Jon, m…®ne Revelesen.
\ip \bd ?R…®m…®rai ramv…ôn k…®mi pa?\bd* R…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e ramv…ôn k…®mi narmam…ô m…ô tukhani n…ôfrak…®sien ye Yesu Kristo. In rorkeikei m…ô tukrasitu ir…ôri…ô mor nhat…ôt…ôyen kap…ôri…ô tukr…®skai, meinai kap…ôri…ô nhat…ôt…ôyen r…®p…ôh n…®skaiyen.
\ip \bd ?N…®mraghien r…®mnhawor p…ôn iran m…®ne ye n…®p…®g r…®m…®rai?\bd* Yesu r…®mamh…ô mamragh m…®n, ai, newk fifti o sikisti ruau…ô muav…ôn ta, Aposol Jon r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e. Jon in yemehu…ô k…®rik kape nim…ôhuak, k…®ni narmam…ô m-fam kape nim…ôhuak kamhasiai in. In rorkeikei m…ô narmam…ô m-fam tukharkun huv…ô kafan nhajounien. K…®ni n…®p…®g nhajounien eiku…ô m…®n…ô tukramu…ô, in rorkeikei m…ô narmam…ô tukharkun nhani-…ôhuyen.
\ip \bd ?R…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e tuk naha?\bd* R…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e mamni-…ôrhav m…ô Yesu in Ji Kughen, k…®ni in Kughen …ôfrak…®s. K…®ni narmam…ô m-fam yam…ô m…®ne kashat…ôt…ô iran tukhav…ôh n…®mraghien rer…®n. K…®ni Jon rorkeikei m…ô tukr…®ni-…ôrhav n…ôvsaoyen kape Yesu yame n…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Matiu m…®ne Mak m…®ne Luk k…®m…®rh…®p…ôh n…®rh…®niyen. K…®ni in rorkeikei m…ô tukr…®ni atuatuk n…ôt…ôr…®gien t…®ks…®n yame narmam…ô kamhani ye Yesu.
\c 1
\s1 N…ôgkiarien kape Kughen r…®mau…ô mor yermam…ô k…®n, in e Yesu
\p 
\v 1 Apa kupan …ôgkap, ye n…®rikakunien, N…ôgkiarien r…®mn…ôm…®r ta.\f + \fr 1:1 \ft Nhag p…®s…®n k…®rik, ramni Yesu Kristo, m…ô ‚ÄúN…ôgkiarien.‚Äù ∆ém-ru Jen 1:1; 1 Jon 1:1; Jon 17:5; Rev 19:13.\f* N…ôgkiarien e r…®mnamar…ô iriu Kughen. K…®ni N…ôgkiarien e, in Kughen.
\v 2 N…®p…®g Kughen r…®p…ôh han…ô norien nar…®mnar, in r…®nar…ô rer…®n ta iriu Kughen.
\v 3 K…®ni Kughen r…®mnor nar…®mnar fam ye n…ôgkiarien a, k…®ni nar…®mnar fam yame Kughen r…®mnor, nar k…®rik m…®n r…®k…ôk yame N…ôgkiarien a r…®m…®p…ôh norien.\x - \xo 1:3 \xt Kol 1:16; 1 Korin 8:6; Hib 1:2 \x*
\v 4 In e, in Nuknei n…®mraghien, k…®ni n…®mraghien e, in n…®kakien yame ram…ôsia-pen narmam…ô m…®fam.\x - \xo 1:4 \xt Jon 5:26; 11:25; 14:6 \x*
\v 5 N…®kakien a ram…ôsia-pen n…ôp…®gn…ôpien, k…®ni n…ôp…®gn…ôpien to r…®p…ôh napitayen.\x - \xo 1:5 \xt Jon 9:5; 12:46 \x*
