\v 18 Narmam…ô to khap…ôh n…®s…ômien Kughen. M…ôr…®g T…®ni Kw…ônkwan K…®rikian…ô ∆ém…ô, yame ram…ôrer ye n…®kar Kughen, in Kughen. In r…®mnor …ôpu Kughen k…®mi …ôtaw…ô k…®ni k…®taw…ô kharkun In.\x - \xo 1:18 \xt 2 Korin 4:6; Kol 1:19; 2:9; Rev 22:4 \x*
\s1 Jon Baptaes ramni m…ô p…ôh nien m…ô in Kristo
