\p M…ôr…®g Jon r…®m…ô, ‚ÄúN…®kam. P…ôh nien m…ô yo Elaeja.‚Äù
\p K…®ni iri…ô k…®m…®saiyoh m…®n in mham…ô, ‚Äú?Tukm…ô p…ôh nien m…ô ik Elaeja, k…®ni ik pa? ?Ik profet kape Kughen yame k…®m…®ni kupan m…ô tukru…ô u…ô?‚Äù\x - \xo 1:21 \xt Dut 18:15 \x*
