\v 26 K…®ni Jon rhorp…®n n…ôgkiarien kap…ôri…ô m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúYo yakamor baptaes ye narmam…ô ye nu, m…ôr…®g yermam…ô k…®rik ram…ôrer ye kwerkwan ir…ômi…ô yame nakseinein In.
\v 27 Yo yakam…ôkupan, kw…ôn a tukr…®kwas…®g, m…ôr…®g In yerp…®r…®g, k…®ni yo yetan…ô …ôm…ô. Yakp…ôh n…ômhenien tuk n…®r…®s…®n-tayen sandel kafan.‚Äù
