\v 14 ‚ÄúApa kupan, Moses r…®mnamar…ô ye t…®p…ôvs…®k, m…®ruk hakt…ô nar yame r…®mnor m…®s…®gov…®n snek k…®n, m…®ruk hakt…ô ye nai.\f + \fr 3:14 \ft In apa kupan Moses r…®m…®k…®r …ôrhav n…ôm…ô Isrel ye kwerm…® n…ôm…ô Ijip, m…ôr…®g n…ôm…ô Isrel k…®mnhani hah Moses m…®ne Kughen. Kughen rher-p…ôn k…®n snek yam…ô m…®ne kas…ôkw…ôpah, k…®m…®s…ôs …ôri…ô. K…®ni narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®sarha-p…ôn mas…ôm nar yame rams…®gov…®n snek, yame Moses r…®m…®ruk hakt…ô, kamhamragh. M…ôr…®g yam…ô m…®ne khap…ôh n…®sarha-p…ônien m…®s…ôm nanm…® snek, kamhamh…ô. ∆ém-ru stori ye Nam 21:4-9. Ik…®n e Yesu ramni m…ô snek ramuh nuhp…®k…®nien k…®n n…ômh…ôyen kape Yesu ye nai kamarkwao k…®n. K…®m…®ruk hakt…ô in, k…®ni narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®sarha-p…ôn m…®s…ôm, kamhamragh.\f* K…®ni ye norien k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô m…®n, tukruk hakt…ô m…®n Yo, Ji Yermam…ô,\x - \xo 3:14 \xt Nam 21:4-9; Jon 8:28; 12:32; 12:24\x*
\v 15 m…ô narmam…ô m-fam yam…ô m…®ne kamhani n…ôfrak…®sien irak tukhav…ôh n…®mraghien rer…®n.
