\c 4
\s1 Yesu ru…®rkun ta norien kape pian Sameria k…®rik
\p 
\v 1 Farisi m…®n…ô k…®m…®s…ôr…®g n…ôgkiarien m…ô Yesu ravi-p…ô narmam…ô khapsaah kamhau…ô tukun, k…®ni In mamor baptaes ir…ôri…ô khapsaah. Namba ir…ôri…ô r…®psaah rapita narmam…ô kape Jon m…®n…ô.
\v 2 (M…ôr…®g n…ôfrak…®sien m…ô p…ôh nien m…ô Yesu r…®mnor baptaes ir…ôri…ô, m…ôr…®g narmam…ô kafan m…®n…ô k…®m…®sor baptaes ye narmam…ô.)
\v 3 K…®ni n…®p…®g Yesu r…®mn…ôr…®g m…ô Farisi m…®n…ô k…®m…®s…ôr…®g n…ôvsaoyen k…®n, r…®m…®t…ôrhav Judia m…®rer…®g-p…ôn apa Galili.
