\v 4 R…®m…ô tukruv…®n apa Galili, m…ôr…®g provins e Sameria ram…ôrer …ôkupan.
\v 5 K…®ni r…®t…ôrhav-p…ô ye taon k…®rik ye Sameria, kamni k…®m…ô Saeka. Taon a, ipak…ô tuk tan…ô k…®rik yame Jekob r…®m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn k…®mi t…®ni a Josef apa kupan.\x - \xo 4:5 \xt Jen 48:22; Jos 24:32\x*
\v 6 Ik…®n aik…®n a, huaru Jekob r…®m…®k…®r kw…ôt…®g nu k…®rik kafan. Yesu r…®mn…ôriw…ôk rapomh ik…®n m…®n…ôp…ôu, k…®ni mu…ô m…ôkw…ôt…ô-p…ôn ye n…®kar kw…ôt…®g nu a, mamap…®s, yerkweiha. \fig Kw…ôt…ôg nu k…®rik|alt="A well" src="HK083B.jpg" size="span" loc="Bottom of page" copy="Horace Knowles" ref="JHN 4:6"\fig*
\p 
\v 7-8 K…®ni kafan narmam…ô m…®n…ô k…®mnhav…ôn apa taon, m…ô tukhav…ôh n…®mr…® n…ôv…®g…®nien. K…®ni pian Sameria k…®rik ramu…ô m…ô tukr…®ruk nu. K…®ni Yesu r…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúEh. Ruk nu m…®v…ôhsi-p…ô k…®mi Yo.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 K…®ni pian Sameria a r…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…ô, ‚Äú!Eh! Ik yem…ô Isrel, k…®ni yo pian Sameria. ?Rhawor e nakam…ôgkiar k…®mi yo?‚Äù Ramni m…ôknak…®n meinai n…ôm…ô Isrel kap…ôri…ô k…®rik nar k…®rik r…®k…ôk tuk nar Sameria.
