\v 10 K…®ni Yesu r…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…ô, ‚ÄúIk nakeinein naha nhag…®n yame Kughen rorkeikei m…ô tukr…®v…ôhsi-pre k…®mik. K…®ni ik nakameinein m…®n Yo. Yo e, yakamaiyoh-pre nu k…®mik. To nakpirkun, nakpiaiyoh-p…ô k…®n nu tuk Yo. K…®ni yakpiv…ôhsi-pre nu m…®ragh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 K…®ni pian a r…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúYemehu…ô. Ik kafam tikikwip…®r r…®k…ôk, k…®ni kw…ôt…®g nu e reiwaiyu p…®k. ?Takhawor-p…ôn iran m…®ne m…®ruk nu m…®ragh e yame nakamni?
\v 12 Apa kupan, r…®ptaw…ô Jekob r…®mnamruk nu eik…®n e nin m…®ne ni kafan kwajikov…ô m…®n…ô, m…®ne ni kau m…®n…ô kafan, k…®ni ai, meighan-p…ô k…®n kw…ôt…®g nu e m…ô nitaw…ô. ?M…ôr…®g rhawor? ?Nakm…ô ik nakehu…ô rapita r…®ptaw…ô Jekob, u…ô?‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 K…®ni Yesu r…®m…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…ô, ‚ÄúNarmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kamhan…®m nu ye kw…ôt…®g…®n e, tukas…ôkeikei m…®s…ôkwakw…ô m…®n.
\v 14 M…ôr…®g narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne tukhan…®m nu m…®ragh yame yakv…ôhsi-p…ôn k…®mi …ôri…ô, to khap…ôh n…®s…ôkwakw…ô-m…®n-ien tuk n…®p…®g k…®rik. Nu yame jakv…ôhsi-p…ôn k…®mi …ôri…ô, in r…ômhen k…®n n…®mr…® nu k…®rik yame ramkwor-kwor apa yerkin n…®p…®g m-fam mamaiyu, m…®v…ôh-si-p…ôn n…®mraghien rer…®n k…®min.‚Äù\x - \xo 4:14 \xt Sam 42:1-2; 63:1, Aes 12:3; 41:17-18; 44:3; 49:10; 55:1; Jer 2:13; 17:13; Jon 7:38\x*
\p 
\v 15 K…®ni pian a r…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúYemehu…ô. V…ôh-si-p…ô-ru nu en k…®mi yo, m…ô jakp…ôh n…ôkwakw…ô-m…®n-ien, p…ôh jakp…ôh nu…ô-m…®nien ik…®n e m…®ruk nu ye kw…ôt…®g…®n e.‚Äù\x - \xo 4:15 \xt Jon 6:34\x*
\p 
\v 16 K…®ni Yesu r…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúYuv…ôn mokr…ôn k…®n kafam huaru, m…®rau…ô.‚Äù
