\v 19 K…®ni pian a r…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…ô, ‚ÄúYemehu…ô, yakw…®rkun m…ô ik profet k…®rik kape Kughen.
\v 20 R…®ptaw…ô m…®n…ô kupan, iri…ô k…®m…®shakt…ô-p…ô ye tukwas e [k…®rau kaw…ôrer ik…®n,\f + \fr 4:20 \ft Iriu kaw…ôrer apa tukwas k…®rik apa Samaria kamni k…®m…ô Gerasim.\f*] mas…ôhuak k…®mi Kughen. M…ôr…®g k…®mi…ô n…ôm…ô Isrel nakamhani m…ô tukam…ôkeikei kav…ôn …ôm…ô apa Jerusalem kam…ôhuak.‚Äù
\p 
\v 21 M…ôr…®g Yesu r…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…ô, ‚ÄúPiahuaru. Ik takam…ôkeikei m…®ni n…ôfrak…®sien ye kafak n…ôgkiarien. N…®p…®g aik…®n tukru…ô yame narmam…ô m-fam takhap…ôh n…®s…ôhuak-…ôm…ô-yen k…®mi Tat…ô Kughen ik…®n e ye tukwas e, mhap…ôh n…®s…ôhuak-…ôm…ô-yen apa Jerusalem.
\v 22 K…®mi…ô n…ôm…ô Sameria, naks…ôhuak pawk k…®mi Kughen, m…ôr…®g nakseinein In. M…ôr…®g k…®maw…ô n…ôm…ô Isrel yakas…ôhuak k…®mi Kughen, mharkun In, meinai swatuk yame Kughen tukr…®v…ôh m…®ragh narmam…ô iran, rams…®-p…ô ir…ômaw…ô.\x - \xo 4:22 \xt Rom 3:1,2; 9:4,5; 15:8,9\x*
\v 23 N…®p…®g ramu…ô - k…®ni ruau…ô ta - yame Nanm…®n kape Kughen tukrasitu ye n…ôm…ôhuak …ôfrak…®s m…®n…ô, mor …ôri…ô tukharkun huv…ô Kughen, m…ô in Kughen …ôfrak…®s, mamor …ôri…ô tuks…ôhuak k…®min yerkiri…ô m…®fam. Meinai Tat…ô Kughen In rorkeikei n…ôm…ôhuak yam…ô m…®ne kas…ôhuak …ôfrak…®s k…®min.
\v 24 Kughen r…®p…ôh norien r…ômhen k…®n n…®prai yermam…ô. In nanm…®n. Ror p…ôn, narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kham…ô tuks…ôhuak k…®min tukas…ôkeikei mas…ôhuak k…®min yerkiri…ô m-fam, ye norien yame Nanm…®n kape Kughen ramasitu ir…ôri…ô, m…ô tukharkun m…ô In Kughen …ôfrak…®s.‚Äù
\p 
\v 25 K…®ni pian a r…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúYo yakw…®rkun m…ô Mesaea tukram…ôkeikei mu…ô. In e, kamokr…ôn k…®n In k…®m…ô Kristo. K…®ni n…®p…®g yame In tukru…ô iran, In tukrhoprai fam n…®prai n…ôgkiarien m…®n…ô k…®mi …ôtaw…ô.‚Äù
