\v 26 K…®ni Yesu r…®m…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…ô, ‚ÄúYo e yakam…ôgkiar k…®mik, Yo e Kristo.‚Äù\x - \xo 4:26 \xt Jon 8:24; 9:35-37\x*
