\v 28 K…®ni pian a, r…ôp…ôh kafan tikikwip…®r, marar mamv…ôn apa ye taon. Mam…ôvsao k…®n k…®mi narmam…ô m…®m…ô,
\v 29 ‚ÄúEh. Hav…ôn-ru m…®s…ôm kw…ôn k…®rik aik…®n a, In ru…®rkun ta norien has m…®n…ô fam yam…ô m…®ne y…®mnamor ye n…®mraghien kafak mamni-p…ô tuk yo. ?Tukm…ô ror in Kristo, u…ô?‚Äù
\v 30 K…®ni narmam…ô khat…ôrhav ye taon, mhav…ôn m…ô tuks…ôm Yesu.
