\v 34 M…ôr…®g Yesu r…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…ô, ‚ÄúKughen r…®mnher-p…ô k…®n Yo yaku…ô, k…®ni n…ôv…®g…®nien nak ror m…ôkneik…®n, m…ô jakamor nar…®mnar fam yame Kughen rorkeikei. K…®ni yakamor fam wok yam…ô m…®n…ô In r…®mnher-p…ô k…®n Yo m…ô jakor, mor naunin ye kafan wok.\x - \xo 4:34 \xt Jon 5:30, 8:29\x*
