\v 42 Mhani-p…ôn tuk pian a mham…ô, ‚ÄúApa kupan, k…®maw…ô y…®mnhani n…ôfrak…®sien iran tuk n…ôvsaoyen yame ik n…®m…®ni-…ôsah-p…ô tuk …ômaw…ô. M…ôr…®g taktakun ai, yakamhani n…ôfrak…®sien iran meinai y…®m…®s…ôr…®g kafan n…ôgkiarien, k…®ni mharkun …ôfrak…®s m…ô in Yermam…ô yame tukr…®v…ôh m…®ragh narmam…ô ye tan…®mtan…ô.‚Äù\x - \xo 4:42 \xt 1 Jon 4:14\x*
\s1 Yesu r…®mnor huv…ô kwajikov…ô kape yemehu…ô k…®rik
