\v 43 Yesu r…®mnamar…ô m…®v…ôh ta n…®p…®g k…®raru, k…®ni ai m…®t…ôrhav m…®v…ôn [iman ik…®n] apa provins Galili.
\v 44 (M…ôr…®g apa kupan in r…®mnamni m…ô, ‚ÄúTukm…ô profet k…®rik kape Kughen, narmam…ô iman ik…®n tukhap…ôh nhasiaiyen In.‚Äù)
\v 45 K…®ni n…®p…®g Yesu r…®t…ôrhav-p…ô Galili, narmam…ô aik…®n k…®mnhani vi vi In meiani in apa kupan iri…ô min k…®mnhav…ôn Jerusalem masor lafet kape Pasova, k…®ni m…®s…ôm nar…®mnar yame In r…®mnor aik…®n.
\v 46 Ror p…ôn, r…®mav…ôn m…®n apa taon e Kena, ye provins Galili. Ik…®n a kupan, In r…®mnor nu rukreik…®n mu…ô mor waen k…®n. K…®ni yemehu…ô k…®rik ramar…ô apa taon p…®s…®n k…®rik e Kapaneam, kafan kwajikov…ô ramh…ô.\x - \xo 4:46 \xt Jon 2:1-11\x*
\v 47 K…®ni yemehu…ô a r…®mn…ôr…®g m…ô Yesu ruat…ôrhav Judia mamu…ô e Galili, m…ôkneik…®n r…®v…ôn m…ôm Yesu, mam…ôkeikei k…®min m…ô tukr…®v…ôn apa Kapaneam mor huv…ô kafan kwajikov…ô. Meinai kafan kwajikov…ô, n…®mh…ôyen r…®neriaji.
