\v 51 N…®p…®g ram…ôriw…ôk han…ô ye swatuk, m…ôm kafan yorwok m…®n…ô, k…®ni iri…ô khani-p…ôn tukun mham…ô, ‚ÄúKafam kwajikov…ô r…®n…ôsan…®n.‚Äù
