\p K…®ni Paelat r…®m…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…ô, ‚ÄúN…®kam. K…®mi…ô atuatuk hak…®r mhav…ôn, m…®s…ôs…®k-p…ôn In ye nai kamarkwao k…®n. M…ôr…®g Yo yakp…ôh n…ôm-p…ônien nar has k…®rik iran.‚Äù
