\v 18 Ye kw…ônmhaan atuatuk a in a, k…®m…®sarkw…ôt…ôr…ôk…®n hakt…ô Yesu ik…®n ye nai kamarkwao k…®n. M…®sarkw…ôt…ôr…ôk…®n m…®n yermam…ô k…®raru. K…®rik ye n…®kar…®n matuk; k…®rik ye mawor. K…®ni Yesu r…®mn…ôker ye kwerkwan.
\p 
\v 19 K…®ni Paelat r…®ni, k…®rai ta n…ôgkiarien k…®rik, karkw…ôt…ôr…ôk…®n hakt…ô ye nai kamarkwao k…®n. N…ôgkiarien a ramni m…ô, ‚ÄúYesu, Yem…ô Nasaret. In King kape n…ôm…ô Isrel.‚Äù\x - \xo 19:19 \xt Jon 19:14,21\x*
\v 20 K…®ni n…ôm…ô Isrel khapsaah k…®m…®s…ôvheik…®n n…ôgkiarien a, meinai ik…®n a, k…®m…®sarkw…ôt…ôr…ôk…®n hakt…ô Yesu ik…®n, ipak…ô …ôm…ô tuk taon. K…®ni n…ôgkiarien a k…®m…®rai ye n…ôgkiarien kape n…ôm…ô Isrel, m…®ne ye n…ôgkiarien kape n…ôm…ô Rom, m…®ne ye n…ôgkiarien kape n…ôm…ô Gris.\x - \xo 19:20 \xt Hib 13:12\x*
\v 21 K…®ni jif pris m…®n…ô kape n…ôm…ô Isrel k…®mnhav…ôn mhani-p…ôn tuk Paelat mham…ô, ‚ÄúTakp…ôh n…®raiyen m…ô ‚ÄòIn e king kape Isrel.‚Äô Rhuv…ô m…ô takrai m…ô, ‚ÄòKw…ôn e in ramni m…ô in king kape n…ôm…ô Isrel.‚Äô‚Äù\x - \xo 19:21 \xt Jon 19:14\x*
\p 
\v 22 M…ôr…®g Paelat r…®m…ô, ‚ÄúN…®kam. Yakw…ôrai, yakw…ôrai.‚Äù
\s1 Mobael m…®n…ô k…®m…®s…ôwhai neip…ôn kape Yesu
\p 
\v 23 K…®ni n…®p…®g mobael m…®n…ô kw…ôs…ôkw…ôt…ôr…ôk…®n-p…ôn ta Yesu ye nai kamarkwao k…®n, k…®ni mhap…®k kafan nar…®mnar, k…®ni m…®s…ôwhai nar…®mnar m…®s…ôtu n…®mr…®n kuas, meinai iri…ô kuas. M…ôr…®g k…®mnhap…ôh n…®s…ôwhaiyen kot apomh kafan. N…®p…ôr…®n …ôm…ô, yame k…®p…ôh n…®jirien.
\v 24 Mhani-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…®n…ô mham…ô, ‚ÄúTo khap…ôh n…®seikusien. P…ôh k…®s…ôs…®k daes tukun. Yermam…ô yame rapita, kafan e kot.‚Äù Nar e r…®t…ôrhav-p…ô mor n…ôgkiarien ye n…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Kughen ru…ô mor n…ôfrak…®sien k…®n, yame ramni m…ô,
\q1 ‚ÄúIri…ô tukhap…®k ta kafak neip…ôn m…®s…ôwhai ir…ôri…ô m…®n…ô.
\q2 K…®ni m…®saruk…®n daes tukun.‚Äù\rq (Sam 22:18)\rq*
\nb Ror m…ôkneik…®n, mobael m…®n…ô k…®m…®sor …ôfrak…®s m…ôknak…®n.\x - \xo 19:24 \xt Jon 19:28,36,37\x*
\s1 Yesu m…®ne kafan mam…ô
\p 
\v 25 K…®ni n…®piraov…®n kuas k…®mnas…ôrer ipak…ô tuk nai kamarkwao k…®n kape Yesu. Iri…ô e: Mam…ô kape Yesu, m…®ne piauni, m…®ne Meri k…®rik m…®n, yame in piraov…®n kape Kleopas, m…®ne Meri p…®s…®n k…®rik, yame in pian Magdala.\x - \xo 19:25 \xt Luk 8:2; Jon 20:1,18\x*
\v 26 K…®ni Yesu rarha-p…ôn m…ôm kafan mam…ô, m…®ne yermam…ô k…®rik kafan yame in rorkeikei p…®k, kaw…ôrer ipak…ô tukun, k…®ni r…®ni-p…ôn tuk kafan mam…ô m…ô, ‚ÄúPian …ôp…ô, kafam en kwajikov…ô.‚Äù
\v 27 M…®ni-p…ôn tuk kw…ôn a m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúKafam en mam…ô.‚Äù K…®ni r…®rikakun ye n…®p…®g a, yermam…ô a kape Yesu ram…ôm huv…ô pian a r…ômhen k…®n mam…ô atuatuk kafan.
\s1 Yesu r…®mamh…ô
\r (Mat 27:45-56; Mak 14:33-41; Luk 23:44-49)
\p 
\v 28 K…®ni kwas…®g ik…®n ye nar…®mnar m…®n…ô a, Yesu ru…®rkun m…ô In r…®n…ôrkin wok yame r…®mau…ô tukun m…ô tukror. K…®ni m…®m…ô ‚ÄúYakn…ôkwakw…ô.‚Äù R…®m…®ni m…ôkneik…®n m…ô tukror n…ôgkiarien k…®rik ye N…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Kughen tukru…ô mor n…ôfrak…®sien k…®n.\f + \fr 19:28 \ft ∆ém-ru profesi k…®rik ye Ol Sam 69:21.\f* \x - \xo 19:28 \xt Jon 17:4\x*
\p 
\v 29 K…®ni kwaji besin k…®rik aik…®n ramkw…ôt…ô, kw…ôvi-p…ôn ta waen …ôkwahir iran. K…®ni iri…ô khar…ôh neip…ôn k…®rik, m…®seires waen k…®n, m…®sark…®s-p…ôn ye nai k…®rik kamni k…®m…ô ‚Äòhisop‚Äô mhav…ôh-si hakt…ô mhav…ôhsi-p…ôn ipak…ô tuk t…®kinher Yesu, m…ô tukr…®n…®m.
\v 30 K…®ni r…ôpaih …ôs…®g…ôv…®n waen, m…®ni m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúR…®nor infamien.‚Äù
\p K…®ni r…®vaag-…ôhu, meighan-p…ôn k…®n n…®mraghien kafan, k…®ni m…®mh…ô.\x - \xo 19:30 \xt Luk 12:50; Jon 4:34; 17:4\x*
\s1 Mobael k…®rik r…®mnhai n…®kar Yesu
\p 
\v 31 Ruau…ô ye n…®p…®g kape napn…ôpen…ôyen, tuk…ôni r…®kwam…®rk…®n, Sabat. (Sabat a in n…®p…®g ehu…ô k…®rik). K…®ni n…ômehu…ô kape n…ôm…ô Isrel k…®mnhap…ôh n…®sorkeikeiyen m…ô n…®prai yermam…ô tukram…ôker ye nai kamarkwao k…®n meriaji-p…ôn Sabat. Ror p…ôn, iri…ô t…®ks…®n k…®mnhav…ôn m…®saiyoh Paelat mham…ô tukrher-p…ôn k…®n mobael m…®n…ô khav…ôn m…®shopr…®r-hopr…®r n…®huris…®r, p…ôh iris…®r tukrh…®mh…ô aihuaa …ôm…ô. K…®ni n…ôm…ô Isrel tukhar…ôh-si ta n…®prairis…®r ye nai kamarkwao k…®n.
\v 32 K…®ni mobael m…®n…ô k…®m…®s…ôkup…ôn m…®shopr…®r-hopr…®r n…®hu yermam…ô mir e kaw…ôker ipak…ô tuk Yesu.
\v 33 Mhau…ô ipak…ô tuk Yesu, m…®s…ôm m…ô In ruamh…ô ta, mhap…ôh n…®shopr…®rien n…®hun.
\v 34 M…ôr…®g iri…ô k…®rik r…®mnhai …ôm…ô n…®kar…®n k…®n kwenhao. ∆ém…ô aik…®n, n…®taw…®n m…®ne nunu iran, iriu kwis k…®m…®waiyu m…®rat…ôrhav ye n…®kar…®n.\x - \xo 19:34 \xt Sek 12:10; 1 Jon 5:6-8; Rev 1:7\x*
\v 35 (K…®ni kw…ôn k…®rik r…®nam…ôrer ipak…ô tukun, m…ôm nar…®mnar m…®n…ô e k…®n n…®mr…®n. K…®ni mamni-…ôrhav n…ôgkiarien yam…ô m…®ne ram…ôfrak…®s. Mamrai-p…ôn ye n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e m…ô k…®mi…ô m…®n takhani n…ôfrak…®sien iran).
\v 36 Nar…®mnar m…®n…ô e k…®mnhat…ôrhav-p…ô m…®sor n…ôgkiarien k…®rik ye N…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Kughen ruau…ô mor n…ôfrak…®sien k…®n, yame ramni m…ô,\x - \xo 19:36 \xt Jon 19: 24,28,37\x*
\q1 ‚ÄúTo iri…ô khap…ôh n…®shop…®r-p…®rien n…®k…ôkrin k…®rik.‚Äù\rq (Eks 12:46; Nam 9:12; Sam 34:20) \rq*
\nb 
\v 37 K…®ni n…ôgkiarien k…®rik m…®n ye N…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Kughen ramni m…ô,
\q1 ‚ÄúIri…ô tuksarha-p…ôn m…®s…ôm yermam…ô yame k…®m…®shai.‚Äù\rq (Sek 12:10) \rq*\x - \xo 19:37 \xt Rev 1:7\x*
\s1 Josef yem…ô Aramatia, m…®ne Nikodimas, k…®m…®werkwaig k…®n n…®prai Yesu
\r (Mat 27:57-61; Mak 15:42-47; Luk 23:50-56)
\p 
\v 38 K…®ni ai, yem…ô Aramatia k…®rik, nhag…®n e Josef, in yermam…ô k…®rik kape Yesu. M…ôr…®g ramerkwaig k…®n m…ô tukp…ôh n…®rkunien m…ô in yermam…ô kafan, meinai ramg…®n k…®n n…ômehu…ô kape n…ôm…ô Isrel. K…®ni in r…®mav…ôn m…ôm Paelat, maiyoh in m…ô tukreighaan k…®n n…®prai Yesu. K…®ni Paelat reighan k…®n, k…®ni Josef r…®v…ôn m…®r…ôhsi-…ôhu.\x - \xo 19:38 \xt Jon 7:13\x*
\p 
\v 39 K…®ni Nikodimas e kupan r…®mav…ôn yenp…®g m…ôm Yesu, in r…®kwas…®g k…®n Josef. Mamrur n…®t…®p k…®rik rukwar k…®n monar pien pien mir e ‚Äòmir‚Äô m…®ne ‚Äòalos.‚Äô N…®t…®p a r…®pam r…ômhen k…®n toti fo kilo\f + \fr 19:39 \ft N…ôgkiarien kape n…ôm…ô Gris ramni ‚Äúwan handred litrai;‚Äù r…ômhen k…®n toti fo kilo.\f*.\x - \xo 19:39 \xt Jon 3:1-2; 7:50\x*
\p 
\v 40 K…®ni iriu k…®r…ôr…ôhsi-ta n…®prai Yesu, m…®r…ôuvr…®g k…®n neip…ôn k…®rik e ‚Äòlinen.‚Äô K…®ni m…®wor-p…ôn monar pien pien ye n…®pran, ram…ôri-p…ôn …ôm…ô norien kape n…ôm…ô Isrel tuk n…®n…®mien yermam…ô.
\v 41 K…®ni ik…®n a k…®m…®ruk hakt…ô Yesu ik…®n, ipak…ô tuk n…ôsimien k…®rik. Ye kw…ônmhaan a, k…®mn…ôpn…ôpein…ô ta ye n…®p…ôg kapier tuk n…®n…®mien yermam…ô, m…ôr…®g k…®p…ôh han…ô n…®n…®m-p…ônien yermam…ô k…®rik aik…®n.
\v 42 Meinai tuk…ôni r…®kwamer k…®n, Sabat kape n…ôm…ô Isrel, Josef m…®ne Nikodimas kwhai m…®ren nar, m…®r…ôm…ô tukr…®n…®m aihuaa …ôm…ô. K…®ni n…®p…ôg kapier a yame kamn…®m yermam…ô ik…®n ipak…ô …ôm…ô. Ror p…ôn, iriu kw…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn n…®prai Yesu aik…®n.
\c 20
\s1 Yesu ramragh m…®n
\r (Mat 28:1-10; Mak 16:1-8; Luk 24:1-12)
\p 
\v 1 Ye Sande, yenp…®g-enp…®g …ôgkap, ramp…®gp…®g han…ô, Meri e pian Magdala r…®mav…ôn ye n…ôpag kapier, k…®n m…ôm m…ô kapier ehu…ô yame k…®mukrai …ôswas…®g-p…ôn n…®p…ôg kapier k…®n, k…®n…ôsok ta k…®n.\x - \xo 20:1 \xt Luk 8:2; Jon 19:25\x* \fig Meri r…®mn…ôm m…ô Yesu r…®rk…ôk ye n…ôpag kapier|alt="Jesus rose again" src="Tomb_d.jpg" size="col" copy="Urs Wegmann" ref="Jon 20:1-9"\fig*
\v 2 M…ôkneik…®n, raiyu, m…®rer…®g m…®v…ôn tuk Saemon Pita m…®ne yermam…ô m…®n k…®rik kape Yesu, yame Yesu rorkeikei p…®k in. K…®ni m…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôriu m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúYermam…ô k…®rik ru…®r…ôhsi-…ôrhav n…®prai Yesu Yermaru ye n…®p…ôg kapier. K…®ni yakeinein m…ô r…®mn…ôr…ôhu hi…ô n…®pran.‚Äù
\p 
\v 3 K…®ni Pita m…®ne yermam…ô k…®rik m…®n kape Yesu, k…®m…®rat…ôrhav m…®rav…ôn m…ô tukw…ôm n…ôpag kapier.
\v 4 K…®m…®waiyu p…®k m…®rav…ôn, m…ôr…®g kw…ôr…ô mir a k…®rik r…®mnaiyu m…ôkupan mapitan k…®n Pita, m…®v…ôn ye n…ôpag kapier.
\v 5 K…®ni mamr…ôm…®r, m…®vaag-p…ôn im…ô, m…ôm neip…ôn huv…ô m…®n…ô e kamni k…®m…ô ‚Äòlinen,‚Äô yame k…®muvr…®g Yesu k…®n k…ôkup…ôn ramswiin. M…ôr…®g r…®p…ôh n…®v…ônien im…ô.
\p 
\v 6 K…®ni Saemon Pita rar…ô mu…ô m…®n, k…®ni mauru-p…ôn apa ye n…®p…ôg kapier, m…ôm neip…ôn m…®n…ô a ramswiin.
\v 7 K…®ni m…ôm m…®n neip…ôn yame k…®muvr…®g kap…ôn kap…ô Yesu k…®n kupan. Neip…ôn a, r…®p…ôh n…ôm…®r-p…ônien tuk neip…ôn t…®ks…®n yame k…®muvr…®g Yesu k…®n; m…ôr…®g k…®mnarp…ôv…®n-arp…ôv…®n huv…ô, kukrai-p…ôn ik…®-p…®s…®n.
\v 8 K…®ni ai yermam…ô kape Yesu yame r…®mnaiyu m…ôkupan ye Pita, in m…®n r…®mnauru-p…ôn ye n…®p…ôg kapier, m…ôm nar…®mnar m…®n…ô a, mamni n…ôfrak…®sien m…ô Yesu r…®m…®mragh m…®n ye n…®mh…ôyen.
\v 9 (Ye n…®p…®g a, iriu k…®rap…ôh n…®rarkun-han…ô-yen n…®prai n…ôgkiarien ye N…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Kughen yame ramni m…ô Yesu tukram…ôkeikei mamragh m…®n ye n…®mh…ôyen).\f + \fr 20:9 \ft Profesi e ram…ôm…®r ye Ol Sam 16:10 m…®ne Aes 53:11.\f* \x - \xo 20:9 \xt Luk 24:25-27,46; Jon 2:22; Wok 2:24-28\x*
\s1 Meri e pian Magdala r…®mn…ôkupan m…ôm Yesu
\r (Mak 16:9-11)
\p 
\v 10 K…®ni yermam…ô mir e kape Yesu k…®m…®rarer…®g m…®rav…ôn im…ôriu ik…®n,
\v 11 m…ôr…®g Meri in r…®mn…ôrer ipak…ô tuk n…®p…ôg kapier mamas…ôk. Mamas…ôk …ôm…ô m…ôkneik…®n, m…ômr…ôm…®r, m…®vaag-p…ôn ye n…ôpag kapier,
\v 12 m…ôm agelo mir k…®raru apa im…ô. Neip…ôn kap…ôriu rhaw…ôn p…®k. Iriu kaokw…ôt…ô aik…®n k…®mn…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn n…®prai Yesu ik…®n. K…®rik ramkw…ôt…ô-p…ôn a k…®m…®r…ôhu kap…ôn kap…ô r…®v…ôn p…ôn ik…®n; k…®ni k…®rik ramkw…ôt…ô-p…ôn a k…®mn…ôr…ôhu n…®hun r…®v…ôn p…ôn ik…®n.
\p 
\v 13 K…®ni iriu kwaiyoh Meri m…®r…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúPian …ôp…ô. ?Nakamas…ôk tuk naha?‚Äù K…®ni in r…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôriu m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúKw…ôr…ôhsi-ta n…®prai Yermaru kafak, k…®ni yakneinein m…ô k…®m…®r…ôhu-p…ôn hi…ô.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 Ru…®ni-ta n…ôgkiarien a, marar, marha-p…ôn m…ôm Yesu ram…ôrer aik…®n. M…ôr…®g in r…®p…ôh n…®rkunien m…ô Yesu.
\v 15 K…®ni Yesu raiyoh in m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúPian …ôp…ô. ?Nakamas…ôk tuk naha? ?Nakamarha-k…®n pa?‚Äù
\p M…ôr…®g Meri, r…®kin ram…ôs…®k m…ô ta m…ô y…ôsim k…®rik, r…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúYemehu…ô. Tukm…ô ik n…®m…®r…ôh n…®pran, m…ôr…ôhu ik…®n pukaa, hajoun k…®n yo p…ôh yakv…ôn m…®r…ôh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 16 K…®ni Yesu r…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…ô, ‚ÄúMeri.‚Äù M…ôkneik…®n Meri rarha-p…ôn, m…ôm, mokr…ôn apomh m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúRaboni.‚Äù (Ye n…ôgkiarien kape n…ôm…ô Isrel, n…®pran r…®m…ô, ‚ÄúYhajoun kafak‚Äù).
\p 
\v 17 K…®ni Yesu r…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…ô, ‚ÄúTakp…ôh n…®rapien Yo, meinai yakp…ôh han…ô n…®v…ônien tuk kafak Tat…ô Kughen. M…ôr…®g ik, yuv…ôn, m…ôm naorahik m…®n…ô m…®ni-…ôsahp…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…ô Yo yaknamrer…®g-p…ôn apa ye rao ye neai tuk kafak Tat…ô, k…®ni In m…®n kap…ômi…ô Tat…ô. In Kughen kafak, k…®ni In m…®n kap…ômi…ô Kughen.‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 K…®ni Meri pian Magdala r…®mav…ôn m…ôm narmam…ô kape Yesu m…®n…ô, m…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…®m…ô, ‚Äú!N…ôm…ô m…®n…ô …ôp…ô! Y…®mn…ôm Yermaru.‚Äù K…®ni m…ôvsao k…®n naha nhag…®n yame Yesu r…®m…®ni-p…ôn tukun.
\s1 Narmam…ô kape Yesu m…®n…ô k…®m…®s…ôm In
\r (Mat 28:16-20; Mak 16:14-18; Luk 24:36-49)
\p 
\v 19 Ye Sande, yenaiyu, narmam…ô kape Yesu m…®n…ô k…®m…®sofug…®n …ôri…ô m…®n…ô apa ye nim…ô k…®rik, k…®ni m…®s…ôtap…®g t…®m t…®m, meinai k…®mnhag…®n k…®n n…ômehu…ô m…®n…ô kape n…ôm…ô Isrel. M…ôkneik…®n, Yesu r…®mau…ô m…ôrer ye kwerkwan ir…ôri…ô, k…®ni m…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…ô, ‚ÄúN…ôm…ôrinuyen tukramar…ô tuk …ômi…ô.‚Äù\x - \xo 20:19 \xt Jon 20:21,26; Jon 14:27; 16:33\x*
\v 20 K…®ni mhajoun kwerm…®n k…®n …ôri…ô, m…®ne n…®kar…®n. K…®m…®s…ôm Yesu Yermaru, r…®kiri…ô ragien p…®k.\x - \xo 20:20 \xt Jon 16:19-22\x*
\p 
\v 21 K…®ni Yesu r…®ni-p…ôn m…®n tuk …ôri…ô m…ô, ‚ÄúN…ôm…ôrinuyen tukramar…ô tuk …ômi…ô. Kafak Tata r…®mnher-p…ô k…®n Yo, k…®ni ye norien k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô m…®n, Yo yakamher-…ôrhav k…®n …ômi…ô m…ô takhat…ôrav mhav…ôn ik…®n m…®n…ô ye tan…®mtan…ô.‚Äù\x - \xo 20:21 \xt Mat 28:19; Jon 3:17; 17:18; 20:19,26\x*
\v 22 R…®m…®ni ta n…ôgkiarien e, mher …ôpu …ôri…ô, m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúHav…ôh Nanm…®n kape Kughen.\x - \xo 20:22 \xt Esik 37:9; Jon 7:39; Wok 2:38; 8:15-17; 19:2; Gal 3:2\x*
\v 23 Tukm…ô nakhar…®s…®n narmam…ô tuk t…ôvhag…ô has kap…ôri…ô, Kughen m…®n tukr…®v…ôh-si ta narp…®nien kap…ôri…ô. K…®ni tukm…ô nakhap…ôh nhar…®s…®nien narmam…ô tuk t…ôvhag…ô has kap…ôri…ô, Kughen tukr…®p…ôh n…®v…ôhsi-tayen narp…®nien kap…ôri…ô.‚Äù\x - \xo 20:23 \xt Mat 16:19; 18:18\x*
\s1 Tomas r…®mn…ôm Yesu k…®n n…®mr…®n
\p 
\v 24 K…®ni yermam…ô k…®rik ye narmam…ô twelef kape Yesu, nhag…®n e Tomas. Kamokr…ôn k…®n in k…®m…ô Didimas. In r…®m…®rk…ôk yen…®p…®g Yesu r…®mat…ôrhav-p…ô tuk …ôri…ô.
\v 25 K…®ni in m…®n…ô t…®ks…®n k…®mnhani-p…ôn tukun mham…ô, ‚ÄúEh. Y…®m…®s…ôm Yesu Yermaru.‚Äù
\p M…ôr…®g Tomas r…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…ô, ‚ÄúTukm…ô yak…ôm tamhek nil k…®n n…®mr…®k m…®rap, k…®ni m…®rap tamhek kwenhao ye n…®kar…®n, m…®pini n…ôfrak…®sien iran. M…ôr…®g tukm…ô yakp…ôh n…ômien, to yakp…ôh n…®niyen n…ôfrak…®sien iran.‚Äù\x - \xo 20:25 \xt Mak 16:11\x*
